2026-05-14T00:06:30.3446459Z 22    <!--
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3446998Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3447675Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3448307Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3450085Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3451070Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3451823Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3452593Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3453370Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3454115Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3454831Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-14T00:06:30.3455387Z 33    -->
